summary: Allows about 75 of Mikan's eyes to be used on female human vampires.
descriptionHtml:
[center][font=Courier New]This mod absolutely requires [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/56056]Mikan's Eyes[/url] and Dawnguard.

I made it so that about 75 of the eyes from Mikan Eyes can work on female human vampires. 

Only took about an hour to do, so I hope you enjoy!

[u][b][color=#ff0000][size=3]Requirements
[/size][/color][/b][/u][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/56056/?]Mikan Eyes[/url]
Dawnguard DLC
